*Mladi* su počeli da se okupljaju u parku. (The young people started to gather in the park.)

*Mlade* su osobe imale sastanak u ponedeljak. (The young people had a meeting on Monday.)

*Mladima* je teško da pronađu posao. (It is hard for the young to find a job.)

*Mladost* je bila divna. (Youth was wonderful.)

*Mladih* je sve više u gradu. (There are more and more young people in the city.)

*Mladom* čoveku je potrebna podrška. (The young man needs support.)